Royce Wallace https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Royce_Wallace 0 Royce Wallace (May 9, 1925 - November 24, 1992) was an American veteran stage and screen actress (Funny Lady) who had a long, distinguished career in films and television from the 1960s through the 1980s. She has appeared mostly in guest roles on Sanford and Son, The Paper Chase, Benson, Soap, Quincy, M.E., and Roots: The Next Generations.
